# Custom email sender component provided by WSO2 team

This is the customization component provided by wso2 team in order to implement supporting of the claims in the email templates.

If you would like to use some custom parameters in the emails you need to do the following things:

1. Add necessary claim url in the following format: `{CLAIM_URL}`
2. Add the following as the 1st two lines:
```
username={user-name}%temp
userstoredomain={userstore-domain}%temp
```

Example:
```
username={user-name}%temp
userstoredomain={userstore-domain}%temp

Hi {first-name}, {http://common.verifone.com/claims/lastname}

Thank you for registering with Verifone.
```
